[normal] Based on 50% of the 320 local councils in England adopting a study, and CSEs experience of studies costing an average of £25,000 adding on £5,000 for local councils own staff time. 2012 NHBC research suggests approximately half of local councils have adopted a local renewable energy target: 
[normal]www.nhbc.co.uk/NewsandComment/Documents/filedownload,47340,en.pdf
[normal] Technical guides to the 
[normal]CfSH
[normal] were produced every year between 2006-2010. In addition to this consultation on the Technical Housing Standards Review, Government ran consultations in 2007 and 2010-11. Details of these can be found here: 
[normal]www.planningportal.gov.uk/buildingregulations/greenerbuildings/sustainablehomes/consultations
